{"tid":1136050,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"C朗：我適應得非常好，退役後考慮執教","createTime":"2019-05-02T17:35:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-03T06:13:35.000Z","uid":173952,"like":25,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"ae7ce7596069faf215648ff123fec6aa3fb737ce","tid":1136050,"uid":173952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-02T17:35:07.000Z","msg":"羅日前接受了西班牙《國家報》的採訪，目前該媒體先放出了一些節選。<br />\n<br />\nC羅說道：&ldquo;我來到到新的俱樂部，我做的第一件事情就是做我自己。我的工作理念一直都沒有變過，你必須謙虛，記住你並不了解任何的事情。如果你聰明的話，你可以利用一些小的細節來自我提高。我在尤文適應得非常好，他們也看見了，我也不是什麼水貨。&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;更衣室裡，我們只會聊足球，還有一些正常的話題。&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\nC羅已經34歲了，在足球外也是一名成功的企業家，但他在挂靴後是否考慮執教？ &ldquo;為什麼不呢。&rdquo;他說道。"},{"pid":"b24899e04003bab8b6de66c094b1bf171fabf386","tid":1136050,"uid":36716,"like":28,"dislike":60,"score":-32,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-05-02T17:39:51.000Z","msg":"祖記正前射手榜3甲不入叫<br />\n適應得好好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n同係皇入26球分別大幾多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，分別叫適應唔到喇下話<br />\n小花就係小花"},{"pid":"b8e5052ad52b1b5f06f1b27770bf7b7ad695af97","tid":1136050,"uid":103230,"like":45,"dislike":1,"score":44,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-02T17:42:01.000Z","msg":"咪教過葡萄牙國家隊<br />\n<br />\n仲用球員兼領隊身份攞埋歐國杯"},{"pid":"3d0973d268f1c555fc89e4a97fad393f247b54d5","tid":1136050,"uid":9256,"like":75,"dislike":1,"score":74,"quote":{"pid":"b8e5052ad52b1b5f06f1b27770bf7b7ad695af97","tid":1136050,"uid":103230,"like":45,"dislike":1,"score":44,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-02T17:42:01.000Z","msg":"咪教過葡萄牙國家隊<br />\n<br />\n仲用球員兼領隊身份攞埋歐國杯"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-02T21:38:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Qv9y1Vz.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQv9y1Vz.gif&h=2b7f8063&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ea28581c2f3cc1c5b6ef16c84e8feab864f8fbb6","tid":1136050,"uid":7206,"like":7,"dislike":12,"score":-5,"quote":{"pid":"b24899e04003bab8b6de66c094b1bf171fabf386","tid":1136050,"uid":36